Today, I‚Äôm launching my first prototype. It‚Äôs just a proof of concept, really. A chance for me to flesh out some half-baked ideas and make them concrete. The results aren‚Äôt very interesting yet, but if you‚Äôd like to know what the technical side of my work looks like, here‚Äôs a sneak peek.

